    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this beauty to believe it! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s still in total showroom condition\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that wonderful new-car smell! I'm honestly a bit sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it just like I did. Shoot me a message if you want to come by and take a look!",
