    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a true collector-grade specimen that looks and smells exactly as it did on the showroom floor. Finished in its factory-original paint with a deep, mirror-like gloss, there isn't a single stone chip or swirl mark to be found. The interior is a masterclass in preservation; the premium leather remains supple with zero bolster wear, and every switch operates with a crisp, tactile click. Mechanically, it is flawless, having been stored in a climate-controlled environment and maintained strictly by the book with a complete paper trail of service records. From the pristine undercarriage to the untouched spare tire, this vehicle represents the absolute pinnacle of its model year. It comes complete with all original keys, the owner's manual set in the leather pouch, and a custom-fitted indoor cover. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a showroom-fresh example.",
      "price": 48500.0,
